        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Examining Educational Redlining in Lending Act </b></p> <p>This bill requires the Consumer Financial Protection Bureau to annually assess and report on the use of educational data in determining a consumer's creditworthiness by an individual offering a consumer financial product or service. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
